org.pikater.shared.database.jpa

Class JPAAttributeMetaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pikater.shared.database.jpa.JPAAbstractEntity
      • org.pikater.shared.database.jpa.JPAAttributeMetaData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<JPAAttributeMetaData>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JPAAttributeCategoricalMetaData, JPAAttributeNumericalMetaData

    @Entity
public class JPAAttributeMetaData
extends JPAAbstractEntity
implements java.lang.Comparable<JPAAttributeMetaData>
    Class JPAAttributeMetaData represents a record about dataset's attribute, containing data about common attribute properties (e.g. whether the attribute is target or not).

    From this class are inherited classes, that store more specific properties based upon attributes type.

    See Also:
    JPAAttributeCategoricalMetaData, JPAAttributeNumericalMetaData

        public boolean isVisuallyCompatible(JPAAttributeMetaData metadata)
